<text>Nicholas Sparks (born 1965) is an American author. 

Nicholas Sparks may also refer to:

*Nicholas Sparks (politician) (1794–1862), land owner and member of the first city council of Ottawa, Canada
*Nick Sparks (Alabama politician), Democratic candidate for 2008 elections for the United States House of Representatives representing Alabama&#x27;s 4th District</text><links>
